Technical Direction: Focus on drip forming and falling for 3 seconds mid-shot
Purpose: Introduce Chekhov's poison
Post: Add text overlay "Day 13 - Still too early"
SHOT_2b - RUNWAY - EMPTY DRYING RACK (4 sec)
