Purpose: Establish Sigrid as protector/mother figure
Post: Add lullaby "Sofðu unga ástin mín, úti regnið grætur"
SHOT_5 - VEO - FJORD WIDE (10 sec)
Prompt: "Aerial view 2000 feet above frozen Westfjords fjord, 60% white ice with black water channels, British steam trawler with black smoke stack visible in distance, tiny snow-covered turf house below almost invisible against white landscape, heavy snowfall reducing visibility"
